{"tid":1277450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"越多白色恐怖加秋後算帳，我們要越團結！","createTime":"2019-07-02T07:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T07:46:31.000Z","uid":23189,"like":209,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f5676a0b7f39efa455b9f5195bbdd38183a72021","tid":1277450,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"無輪大家有冇發夢，都想大家可以幫啲發過夢嘅嘢去對抗依啲白色恐怖同秋後算帳！<br />\n大家由今日起全身黑衫黑褲同戴埋口罩去繼續日常生活，包括返工放工行街睇戲食飯！<br />\n就算無黑衫都戴上黑絲帶同戴口罩去支持發夢嘅所有人！<br />\n俾狗逗就俾狗逗，俾人鬧就俾人鬧！<br />\n要向夢境嘅人講「You are not alone」，同當權者同維穩機械講「如果佢哋係暴徒，我哋個個都係暴徒」<br />\n<br />\n進一步嘅話可以全副gear上哂身，然後繼續生活？趁建制班友未通過「反蒙面法」<br />\n<br />\n觀迎大家繼續討論！"},{"pid":"cd58f0176031646fd43e846a46d97955359ff410","tid":1277450,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db9521b1ccc77f54751b0ce1baecf39707679a3b","tid":1277450,"uid":250951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"記得清手機所有記錄位置既apps 緩存<br />\nsim卡報失等<br />\nd衫褲鞋可以燒毀/剪爛就盡量整"},{"pid":"8bbec25411a513211941d894fd498ef561494aba","tid":1277450,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dbb809ffcddf8a3bc93766ffd24101998b089fc","tid":1277450,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:53:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"508866971e0c19027f024324580f36c70278a611","tid":1277450,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">得閒唔該幫手推一下 等更多義士睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「長期置頂」夢遊後執手尾須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276769</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"31b12b1ee41c647cb62cd58988bf5af191844650","tid":1277450,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:55:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff51b0d6